headline: Paychex (NASDAQ:PAYX) Reports Q4 CY2025 In Line With Expectations
summary: Human capital management company Paychex (NASDAQ:PAYX) met Wall Streets revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 18.3% year on year to $1.56 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.26 per share was 2.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
